description: His-Biotin-His Ubiquitin was overexpressed in various fission yeast (S. pombe) genetic backgrounds to identify ubiqutinated proteins. Normalizing to bait (ubiquitin) across samples provided insight into relative changes in ubiquitination with loss of deubiquitinases (DUBs), yielding putative DUB substrates.
